fields.summary: Removed articles on manufacturing option not working
fields.description:
When we import a manufacturing specification where an article has been removed from an option - the relation is not removed in the database.

Currently we have 51 orders in production where this is the case.

This in turn causes the SCSC detailed composition export to fail due to a mismatch between ordered articles and articles on the option. (Errors are in PMT)





SQL to get duplicated orders:
select 
	o.OrderNumber,
	count(distinct moa.ArticleId) as ArticleDiff
from [Order] o
join ManufacturingSpecification m on m.OrderId = o.Id
join ManufacturingOption mo on mo.ManufacturingSpecificationId = m.Id
join ManufacturingOptionArticle moa on moa.ManufacturingOptionId = mo.Id
left join OrderArticle oa on oa.OrderId = o.Id 
 and oa.ArticleId = moa.ArticleId
where oa.ArticleId is null
group by o.OrderNumber
